WEBVTT

00:00:07.065 --> 00:00:09.489
MISTER BIRMAN TAPE NUMBER THREE.

00:00:09.968 --> 00:00:11.447
SO ikh halt

00:00:11.638 --> 00:00:14.264
ven ikh hob gearbet bay aza LINE,

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:15.901
vu zey hobn gevolt,

00:00:15.975 --> 00:00:18.283
un mit di vaser vos zey hobn undz,

00:00:18.283 --> 00:00:20.925
zeyer a sakh zenen groyse artistn geven

00:00:20.925 --> 00:00:24.086
di doytshe, zey hobn gehat a fargenign tsu mordeven yidn.

00:00:24.126 --> 00:00:27.523
s'nisht keyn vunder vos s'iz arayngegangen in kop arayn zayn propagande

00:00:27.523 --> 00:00:29.759
az der yid iz dos ergste vos iz.

00:00:29.759 --> 00:00:32.442
di gantse velt laydt fun yidn,

00:00:32.442 --> 00:00:34.092
zeyer a shvere dos.

00:00:34.183 --> 00:00:38.395
azoy az tomer iz eyner raykh geven hobn zey gezogt az ale yidn zenen raykh,

00:00:38.554 --> 00:00:42.530
azoy m'hot oysgezukht fun unter der erd ruzhnerley verter az m'zol,

00:00:42.537 --> 00:00:44.795
az mir zoln, di polyakn zoln hobn

00:00:44.795 --> 00:00:47.559
a a a grunt

00:00:47.683 --> 00:00:49.331
a GROUND tsu tsum

00:00:49.573 --> 00:00:50.950
tsu zidlen UNK.

00:00:52.037 --> 00:00:55.726
farshteyst ikh dertseyl dem fal un dort hob ikh gearbet a lengere tsayt.

00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:58.022
nakher iz gevorn nokh erger.

00:00:58.298 --> 00:01:02.645
iz hot men gelebt bloyz fun dem shmugl, m'hot badorfn batsoln far dem shmugl.

00:01:02.955 --> 00:01:09.617
un vos hot men getun mit dem vos m'hot gekoyft bay zey? iz geven spetsyele yidn velkhe zey hobn dos opgegebn, zey hobn gehat a kontakt mit di

00:01:09.617 --> 00:01:10.849
mit di shmugler,

00:01:10.849 --> 00:01:12.587
fun di andere zayt,

00:01:12.587 --> 00:01:15.065
di kristn hobn gants gut bakrign batsolt,

00:01:15.072 --> 00:01:17.749
un yeder hot zikh gekoyft a bisl, ikh veys a

00:01:18.177 --> 00:01:20.688
a tsvey liter, dray liter, fir liter,

00:01:20.688 --> 00:01:22.299
aza un -za

00:01:22.299 --> 00:01:24.060
veyts oder korn,

00:01:24.083 --> 00:01:27.969
un m- m'iz aroyf UNK spetsyele mentshn vos hobn gehat gehat milerlekh,

00:01:27.969 --> 00:01:29.190
vos molt.

00:01:29.331 --> 00:01:30.962
kleyne hent milerlekh.

00:01:31.356 --> 00:01:34.939
un un mit zey iz men aroyf tsu zey, m'hot zey epes gegebn,

00:01:34.939 --> 00:01:38.522
hobn zey opgemolt, m'hot gehat, m'hot fun derfun gekokht zup.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.272
dos iz geven undzer esn, zup.

00:01:41.835 --> 00:01:44.073
iz dos shoyn a vaytere zakh,

00:01:44.653 --> 00:01:46.886
ikh eb shoyn onheybn tsu farkrikhn,

00:01:46.886 --> 00:01:49.029
der hunger iz gegangen azoy groys

00:01:49.029 --> 00:01:52.376
az mentshn zenen shoyn geshtorbn far hunger, tsun ersht hobn zey ayngefangen,

00:01:52.450 --> 00:01:55.256
s'geven, zey hobn ayngefangen oys tsu farkoyfn

00:01:55.256 --> 00:01:56.831
vos zey hobn in shtub,

00:01:57.023 --> 00:02:01.264
veyst dos betgevant, nisht dos betgevant, dos ibertsug fun betgevant.

00:02:01.264 --> 00:02:03.480
zey muzn dokh hobn vos tsu tsudekn zikh.

00:02:03.891 --> 00:02:07.091
un andere zakhn azelkhe vos m'hot gekent farkoyfn.

00:02:07.788 --> 00:02:11.310
un demolt iz shoyn geven shlakht, m'hot dokh nisht gekent farkoyfn

00:02:11.367 --> 00:02:14.275
zikh aleyn, vayl zey hobn nisht gehat azoy fil farkoyft,

00:02:14.275 --> 00:02:15.714
zey hobn shoyn nisht vos tsu farkoyfn.

00:02:16.142 --> 00:02:18.903
un azelkhe mentshn, zey hobn ongehoybn tsu shtarbn far hunger.

00:02:19.888 --> 00:02:22.379
un Varshe iz geven a spetsyele geto,

00:02:22.521 --> 00:02:26.059
ikh far derfar nisht far vayl ikh bin geven in Varshe adurkh gemakht,

00:02:26.082 --> 00:02:28.877
nor keyn shum geto iz nisht geven azoy tragish

00:02:28.984 --> 00:02:32.775
vi in Varshe, Varshe iz geven zeyer a. geven a kleyne mark,

00:02:32.865 --> 00:02:36.414
zenen geshtanen dortn yidn velkhe zey hobn opgekoyft

00:02:36.414 --> 00:02:39.390
un zey hobn gehat kontaktn mit di shmuglers,

00:02:39.497 --> 00:02:42.646
un zey hobn opgekoyft, oder hobn zey bay di bay epes fardint,

00:02:42.670 --> 00:02:46.269
hobn zey gekent koyfn a bisl korn, veyts un hobn a bisl zup.

00:02:46.269 --> 00:02:49.433
azoy iz gegangen der handl. un tsvishn zey ale iz geven

00:02:49.433 --> 00:02:51.286
oyf dem mark eyner vos er hot

00:02:51.394 --> 00:02:55.404
iz im ayngefaln, ken zayn er iz geven in di barazhe far di krig,

00:02:55.461 --> 00:02:57.660
iz im ayngefaln er zol opkoyfn

00:02:57.660 --> 00:03:00.891
ho- dos, ibertsug, laylekher,

00:03:00.891 --> 00:03:02.621
ibertsug ruzhne, un

00:03:02.621 --> 00:03:04.207
un fun dem hot er gemakht

00:03:04.207 --> 00:03:05.684
gedenk ikh azoy vi haynt,

00:03:05.684 --> 00:03:13.412
zibetsik tsentimeter oyf zibetsik, firkantike shtiklekh, un er hot gehat a kleyne, aza umlegale farberay.

00:03:13.412 --> 00:03:15.707
vos er hot nokh gehat efsher fun frierte.

00:03:15.707 --> 00:03:18.559
un er hot zikh opgefarbt blumen, andere zakhn,

00:03:18.559 --> 00:03:21.057
un s'gevorn farkoyft in kristlekhe gegnt arayn.

00:03:21.057 --> 00:03:27.031
far di poyern, far di far di veyst dokh vos zey voynen in UNK, zey hobn lib gehat hobn tikhlekh oyfn kop.

00:03:27.031 --> 00:03:29.238
un dos iz geven iz gegangen aza handl.

00:03:29.363 --> 00:03:33.089
un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu farkoyfn fun zikh oykh dos, ikh hob oykh UNK,

00:03:33.089 --> 00:03:35.482
tsi zibetsik, ikh bin shoyn gelegn in roytn,

00:03:35.708 --> 00:03:40.174
un hot di froy gegebn a bafel di shlus.

00:03:40.416 --> 00:03:43.785
keyn shum farkoyfn nisht, m'muz aroysgeyn zukhn azoy vi,

00:03:43.791 --> 00:03:48.392
der shteyt un der shteyt un handlt oyfn mark, efsher vestu kenen ergets zikh tsukrign.

00:03:48.702 --> 00:03:53.314
ikh hob zikh oysgefunen fun vant dos shtamt un vu er tut ahin di skhoyre.

00:03:53.314 --> 00:03:57.009
bin ikh mir nisht geshtanen oyfn mark gevart biz s'kumt mir tsu a froy

00:03:57.009 --> 00:03:58.283
mit a laylekh,

00:03:58.283 --> 00:04:00.508
nor ikh bin mir aroys in di gasn arayn.

00:04:00.582 --> 00:04:01.706
in geto,

00:04:01.746 --> 00:04:05.469
eyder di froy iz tsugekumen tsu dem Luvne, tsu dem hoypt,

00:04:05.509 --> 00:04:08.374
hob ikh oysgek- oysfarkoyft far im,

00:04:08.374 --> 00:04:12.812
un a bisl biliker, un tsugegangen tsu dem farkoyfer, er hot mir gerufn a shniter,

00:04:12.812 --> 00:04:16.449
un ikh hob far- farkoyft im a bisele tayere ober azoy hob ikh gemakht,

00:04:16.449 --> 00:04:17.951
in di shlekhte tsayt

00:04:17.951 --> 00:04:21.394
hot men gekent nor fun di zup, keyn broyt iz shoyn nisht geven, m'hot gelebt.

00:04:21.394 --> 00:04:24.862
geven zeyer shlakht. dernokh hot zikh shoyn ongehoybn a

00:04:24.862 --> 00:04:27.629
a tragedye vos der oylem hot ongehoybn

00:04:27.629 --> 00:04:33.231
tsu shtarbn far hunger, der tifus iz geven geven a a plamiste tifus, nisht keyn

00:04:33.231 --> 00:04:34.832
a proste tifus,

00:04:35.260 --> 00:04:38.123
un fun tifus iz men geshtorbn fun

00:04:38.196 --> 00:04:39.979
un di laylekher,

00:04:38.803 --> 00:04:41.716
vu hostu gevoynt in di zelbe tsayt?

00:04:40.778 --> 00:04:43.370
ikh hob gevoynt Frentshishkan akht un tsvontsik.

00:04:43.883 --> 00:04:45.520
aleynt mitn vayb?

00:04:45.267 --> 00:04:48.343
ikh a- mit di froy, yo, un der bruder hot men

00:04:48.343 --> 00:04:52.907
dem bruder dem der vos er hot gearbet mit mir tsuzamen, er hot zi gehat dort geheyrat,

00:04:52.907 --> 00:04:58.406
un er hot gevoynt nokh dem heyratn, hot er ge- nokh di khasene, hot er gevoynt oyf a tsveyt gegnt, oyf der Pave gas.

00:04:58.530 --> 00:05:02.557
Pave gas iz geven a groyse tfise, veyst vos a tfise iz?

00:05:03.103 --> 00:05:07.096
iz iz er hot gevoynt oyf a hoykhn shtok, dray shtok,

00:05:07.255 --> 00:05:09.876
di doytshe hobn geflegt arayn tsu khapn mentshn,

00:05:09.876 --> 00:05:11.163
arayntsunemen,

00:05:11.372 --> 00:05:15.343
un zey hobn mir ruzhnelrley drayerayner az m'vet zey avekshikn

00:05:15.343 --> 00:05:23.617
in di andere lender, zey zoln araynbrengen dos guts, dos hob un guts vos zey hobn, vet men zey avekshikn keyn Amerike, keyn Vin dort, mentshn hobn zikh geshtelt, raykhe mentshn.

00:05:23.995 --> 00:05:26.554
di ershte tsaytn iz ongegangen aza

00:05:26.745 --> 00:05:30.716
zey hobn geshikt avek mentshn. bikhdey m'zol krign briv arayn in geto arayn,

00:05:30.716 --> 00:05:33.079
az mentshn raykhe, ver es laydt,.

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:36.319
o hobn gehat groyse gesheftn, zey hobn dokh, yeder hot dokh gehat a bisl

00:05:36.319 --> 00:05:38.670
gold, a fingerlekh, zeygerlekh,

00:05:38.997 --> 00:05:46.655
farshteyst, un hobn zey azoy tsugefirt az mentshn zenen arayn in di tfi- nakher hobn zey gezen az s'geyt shoyn tsu fil,

00:05:46.655 --> 00:05:48.545
az s'heybt on tsu brengen tsu fil,

00:05:48.545 --> 00:05:52.305
hobn zey ongehoybn di mentshn oysshisn, shteln tsu der vant in Pavyak,

00:05:52.395 --> 00:05:55.527
di tfise hot geheysn Pavyak, Pavyak tfise.

00:05:56.108 --> 00:05:59.646
un mayn bruder hot gevoynt oyf a hoykhn shtok, oyf dray shtok.

00:05:59.972 --> 00:06:04.691
un der fun dem fentster hot er gezen vos far a khazeray di doytshn makhn.

00:06:04.866 --> 00:06:08.339
hobn zey gegebn a bafel ale zoln arop fun di ale shtokn,

00:06:08.339 --> 00:06:11.069
un arayngeyn in andere gegnter arayn voynen.

00:06:11.127 --> 00:06:15.947
der bruder farlozt di dire un er iz arayn tsu mir, dort vu ikh hob gevoynt mit der froy, ikh mit der froy.

00:06:16.037 --> 00:06:18.461
az m'voynt Franshishkana akht un tsvontsik.

00:06:18.244 --> 00:06:23.223
antshuldik mir, d- ir host, ir hot gezogt, nokh di khasene

00:06:23.223 --> 00:06:25.147
host gevoynt noent tsu

00:06:25.147 --> 00:06:26.775
di vayb's eltern.

00:06:26.775 --> 00:06:29.008
yetst bistu tsurik in der heym?

00:06:26.905 --> 00:06:30.156
ah ah ah ah yo. ober ikh ken tsurik tsien?

00:06:30.297 --> 00:06:34.729
demolt ven ikh hob gevoynt in dem kristlekhn gegnt noent di froy's eltern,

00:06:34.819 --> 00:06:36.714
iz hot men gekrign

00:06:36.714 --> 00:06:38.207
az ale yidn

00:06:38.207 --> 00:06:40.769
vos zey voynen in kristlekhe gegntn

00:06:40.810 --> 00:06:43.169
zoln zikh arayntsien in geto arayn.

00:06:43.169 --> 00:06:44.938
di geto iz shoyn geven demolts fertik.

00:06:45.501 --> 00:06:50.121
un m'zol ariberlozn alts, a khuts bay dos perzenlekhe vos m'hot bay zikh,

00:06:50.121 --> 00:06:52.852
un farlozn di dires, takesh fun demolt bin ikh arop

00:06:52.943 --> 00:06:55.249
fun dem shtub vu ikh hob gehat gedungen,

00:06:55.255 --> 00:06:58.727
un ikh bin mir arayn dort vu ikh hob gefirt dem varshtat a mol.

00:06:58.727 --> 00:07:02.963
un der bruder azoy fun Pavyak iz er arop, vu s'geven der Pavyater tfise,

00:07:02.963 --> 00:07:06.437
un m'hot zikh dortn zikh, er hot farnumen a shtub un ikh a shtub.

00:07:07.354 --> 00:07:09.744
dos iz geven nokh in frierdike.

00:07:10.476 --> 00:07:12.784
farshteyst? azoy az der bruder

00:07:12.784 --> 00:07:14.688
dort gemuzt farlozn di dire.

00:07:14.627 --> 00:07:19.936
zog mir, mentshn zenen gekumen FROM andere erter in Poyln?

00:07:18.492 --> 00:07:21.608
mentshn zenen gekumen fun zeyer a sakh erter.

00:07:21.985 --> 00:07:24.639
der gantser gegnt arum un arum Varshe

00:07:24.639 --> 00:07:27.212
hot men geshikt fun ale kleyne shtetlekh arayngeshikt.

00:07:27.212 --> 00:07:29.470
shtel dikh for vos in geto hot zikh gemakht,

00:07:29.511 --> 00:07:32.747
az s'arayngekumen toyznter un toyznter mentshn.

00:07:32.747 --> 00:07:35.464
arayn eng, s'nisht geven vu tsu voynen, vu tsu shlofn,

00:07:35.464 --> 00:07:37.650
un der tifus iz arumgegangen.

00:07:37.650 --> 00:07:40.493
ven ikh hob der tifus, ikh hob zikh tsugegreyt tsum tifus,

00:07:40.493 --> 00:07:42.797
vi er iz geven azoy, m'iz geven azoy

00:07:42.797 --> 00:07:45.159
shoyn tsurikgesh- -rays tsurikgeshtelt,

00:07:45.159 --> 00:07:46.582
in azelkhe

00:07:46.622 --> 00:07:48.602
umshtendn hot men gevoynt,

00:07:48.602 --> 00:07:51.358
az s'iz bet aykh iber farloyzt gevorn.

00:07:51.550 --> 00:07:53.046
layzik, veyst dokh.

00:07:53.271 --> 00:07:56.719
un ven hob ikh gekoyft ayngekoyft di ale vaysverg

00:07:56.719 --> 00:07:58.558
tsu makhn farkoyfn im,

00:07:58.558 --> 00:07:59.997
zenen zey geven ful

00:08:00.021 --> 00:08:02.405
ful un ikh hob es getrogn oyf zikh,

00:08:02.405 --> 00:08:06.464
un ikh bin mir nokh dem gemuzt, az ikh tsugegreyt tsum shniter, mit di layz,

00:08:06.464 --> 00:08:10.134
zenen geven di shtubn zenen geven shreklekh farlayzt, di tifus hot gepanevet,

00:08:10.134 --> 00:08:11.594
keyn esn iz nisht geven,

00:08:11.594 --> 00:08:15.489
hot zikh ongehoybn di khasene, tog teglekh iz gelign oyf der gas,

00:08:15.546 --> 00:08:19.067
oyf der gas, un toyte mentshn tsugedekt mit tsaytunger,

00:08:19.191 --> 00:08:22.622
un s'gekumen dernokh veyst dokh fun gutn ort,

00:08:22.622 --> 00:08:25.800
a groyse vogn hot tsugenumen ale meysim,

00:08:25.823 --> 00:08:28.005
tsunoyfgenumen fun gas tsu gas,

00:08:28.005 --> 00:08:31.233
un avekgefirt, gemakht a groysn keyver far di ale.

00:08:31.932 --> 00:08:36.144
dos iz aribergegangen, demolts iz shoyn geven a groyse tragedye in geto.

00:08:36.909 --> 00:08:37.915
geferlekh!

00:08:38.361 --> 00:08:41.662
un s'gegangen zeyer a la- a lange tsayt un

00:08:41.684 --> 00:08:44.733
un ikh hob zikh di gantse tsayt, undz hobn zikh gerufn

00:08:44.757 --> 00:08:47.839
s'geven f- azelkhe gemakhte doytshishe

00:08:48.064 --> 00:08:49.782
FACTORIES iz geven,

00:08:49.782 --> 00:08:53.103
in geto, in groysn geto, s'geven a kleyn geto oykhet.

00:08:53.903 --> 00:08:56.428
oyb ikh eb onrufn di gas vu s'hot zikh

00:08:56.535 --> 00:08:58.776
fareynikt mitn tsveytn geto,

00:08:58.776 --> 00:09:02.689
eyn geto iz geven in di andere zayt Lesh gas, Leshno,

00:09:02.830 --> 00:09:06.418
un di zayt, di groyse geto, iz geven mayn zayt vu ikh hob gevoynt.

00:09:06.795 --> 00:09:09.711
un az nisht adurkh tsu hakn di kristlekhn gegnt

00:09:09.711 --> 00:09:14.540
fun eyn geto in tsveytn, hobn zey gemakht a groyse brik, a hoykhe brik, a BRIDGE,

00:09:14.608 --> 00:09:18.297
un di yidn hobn gekent bavegn zikh fun eyn geto un tsveytn arayn.

00:09:18.642 --> 00:09:20.863
tsum kleynem geto un tsum groysn geto.

00:09:21.342 --> 00:09:23.681
s'zol nisht zayn keygn, vos hob ikh dos gevolt zogn?

00:09:24.025 --> 00:09:26.401
iz der der der hunger demolts

00:09:26.401 --> 00:09:31.359
iz geven geferlekh, hot men dortn in dem kleynem geto hob ikh geflegt a mol zikh ariber shpatsirn,

00:09:31.821 --> 00:09:35.359
un oykh geven di zelbe tsores iz geven, shver gearbet,

00:09:35.702 --> 00:09:37.670
iz di, hot zikh oyfgeefnt

00:09:37.677 --> 00:09:40.877
iz hot zikh oyfgeefnt, oyf di tsvey getos zey hobn zikh geefnt

00:09:40.883 --> 00:09:44.719
eyner hot zikh geefnt oyf mayn gegnt, in mayn groysn geto,

00:09:44.719 --> 00:09:47.880
hot zi geheysn, a doytshisher firme, s'hot geheysn Bauer,

00:09:48.443 --> 00:09:53.713
un er hot farnumen a gantser gas, eyn zayt gas hot er in gantsn farnumen, di ale hayzer,

00:09:53.713 --> 00:09:56.109
un dort hot men ongehoybn tsu tsunemen

00:09:56.109 --> 00:09:57.566
yidn tsu der arbet,

00:09:57.589 --> 00:10:01.981
un zey hobn veyst dokh, di yidn, un undz ze'mir shoyn geven nisht keyn vilde,

00:10:01.981 --> 00:10:06.234
vayl di mentshn velkhe zenen nisht geven basheftikt in geto, m'hot zey nor gekhapt oyf arbet oder

00:10:06.234 --> 00:10:12.180
m'hot nokh dem, s'nokh dem geven khaperay, m'hot avek geshit in di lagern, dos hob ikh nisht bamerkt, vayl dos hot men zeyer a sakh

00:10:12.372 --> 00:10:14.897
a sakh forgekumen, ikh vel dir nakher dertseyln,

00:10:15.358 --> 00:10:19.435
azoy az dem

00:10:19.543 --> 00:10:20.839
yo, di

00:10:20.893 --> 00:10:22.750
di gantse gas Bauer.

00:10:22.125 --> 00:10:26.017
yo di gantse gas Bauer, un dort hot gearbet mayn's a shvoger, dos sh-

00:10:26.023 --> 00:10:28.483
froy's a a bruder,

00:10:28.483 --> 00:10:32.399
un er hot gehat a gevise opteylung fun HANDSCHUH lederne HANDSCHUHS,

00:10:32.399 --> 00:10:34.252
hot er oysgearbet un,

00:10:34.275 --> 00:10:39.871
s'gevorn opgeshikt tsu di doytshn di gantse zakh, ikh veys nisht far vos, efsher in di shtet arayn tsu farkoyfn dos,

00:10:39.962 --> 00:10:43.246
un m'hot oysgearbet di hent- un ikh hob im gebetn er zol mikh tsunemen.

00:10:43.725 --> 00:10:44.866
er zol mir,

00:10:43.877 --> 00:10:44.866
du host gearbet?

00:10:45.025 --> 00:10:47.991
leder HANDSCHUH, veyst dokh leder GLOVES.

00:10:47.991 --> 00:10:51.279
hentshkes, oyf yidish hentshkes, ober ikh hob gevolt zogn in doytshe.

00:10:50.728 --> 00:10:51.864
UNK.

00:10:51.808 --> 00:10:53.830
HANDSCHUH GLOVES hobn zey ge-

00:10:52.956 --> 00:10:53.827
YEA.

00:10:53.830 --> 00:10:55.644
iz azoy iz

00:10:55.644 --> 00:10:59.244
iz yo, hob ikh dort, hot er mikh arayngenumen.

00:10:59.385 --> 00:11:01.854
un yeder vos iz geven basheftikt in azan

00:11:01.854 --> 00:11:05.339
opteylung, s'nisht a opteylung, in gantsn gegnt,

00:11:05.339 --> 00:11:08.300
hot er gehat aza karte ongehongen,

00:11:08.300 --> 00:11:11.912
un der numer mayner az ikh bin basheftikt bay di doytshn,

00:11:11.912 --> 00:11:16.097
un m'ken mikh nisht khapn oyf keyn, avektsufirn in di lager arayn.

00:11:16.097 --> 00:11:18.180
undz zenen geven legale arbeter.

00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:19.257
nu shoyn.

00:11:19.483 --> 00:11:22.430
un dort hot men undz tsugegebn zup, s'geven a kokh,

00:11:22.437 --> 00:11:24.214
m'hot tsugegebn a shtikl broyt,

00:11:24.214 --> 00:11:25.687
nokh undz alemen

00:11:26.453 --> 00:11:27.893
iz shoyn der y- der

00:11:27.893 --> 00:11:30.952
der vilder hot men gerufn iz shoyn nisht geven keyn

00:11:30.992 --> 00:11:33.331
keyn legale SHOPn doytsh,

00:11:33.692 --> 00:11:37.786
hobn mentshn dortn zikh bahaltn, vayl m'hot gevust m'vet zey khapn.

00:11:38.502 --> 00:11:41.755
un a sakh hobn aropgekumen nokh dem di politsey,

00:11:41.755 --> 00:11:42.962
un doytshn,

00:11:42.962 --> 00:11:46.142
m'hot ongehoybn khapn di mentshn, shoyn nisht oyf keyn arbet

00:11:46.142 --> 00:11:48.552
nor m'hot shoyn ongehoybn khapn oyf transportn.

00:11:48.913 --> 00:11:53.902
transportn, di ershte tsayt hot men gekhapt transportn, zey hobn oysgeleydikt di dires.

00:11:53.942 --> 00:11:55.854
undz zenen mir geven legal,

00:11:55.854 --> 00:11:58.250
iz in di aroys geleydikte dires

00:11:58.250 --> 00:12:00.411
iz nokh gelign ruzhnerley

00:12:00.411 --> 00:12:02.087
VALUABLE zakhn,

00:12:02.262 --> 00:12:06.913
vos m'hot dokh nisht, m'hot gekhapt, m'hot zey aropgeshlept mit klep, m'hot es,

00:12:04.962 --> 00:12:08.668
ven hot dos ongeheybt tsu pasirn?

00:12:07.662 --> 00:12:10.586
dos hot zikh ongehoybn shoyn gants shpet.

00:12:10.586 --> 00:12:15.013
ven ikh bin dokh nokh geven. in dray un fertsikstn yor in may hot men mikh ersht gekhapt.

00:12:15.036 --> 00:12:17.235
azoy ikh hob adurkh gemakht di gantse

00:12:17.235 --> 00:12:19.485
az s'iz shver di peryodn

00:12:19.592 --> 00:12:23.501
biz ontsunemen di tsaytn dem yor, zeyer shver.

00:12:23.507 --> 00:12:25.323
azoy az

00:12:25.347 --> 00:12:29.225
un di mentshn vos iz gevorn gekhapt in di hayzer in di baheltenishn,

00:12:29.225 --> 00:12:33.755
hobn men gesh- tsugeshikt umshlag plats un m'hot ongehoybn avek tsu shikn shoyn

00:12:33.755 --> 00:12:37.502
oyf ruzhnerley kontsentratsyes lagern, s'geven zeyer noent,

00:12:37.502 --> 00:12:40.008
a kontsentratsye iz geven in Lublin, zenen geven

00:12:40.008 --> 00:12:43.430
Maydanek, s'geven Aushvits, azoy p- un alts in Poyln.

00:12:43.318 --> 00:12:47.193
mentshn hopn gevusn vu zey geyen? vu m'nemt zey?

00:12:45.006 --> 00:12:48.909
mentshn mentshn hobn ge- mentshn hot men shoyn gevust.

00:12:48.909 --> 00:12:51.919
far vos vos hot men gevust? vi azoy zey hobn gevust?

00:12:50.153 --> 00:12:51.665
ir ir hot gevusn?

00:12:52.228 --> 00:12:55.040
gevis, vayl vayl zest dokh ikh hob mikh nisht geshtelt.

00:12:55.114 --> 00:12:57.841
ikh hob gevust az m'geyt in di la- in di toyt-lagern arayn.

00:12:57.865 --> 00:13:02.668
vos iz geven? zey hobn genumen mentshn avekgeshikte

00:13:02.758 --> 00:13:04.574
un geheysn dortn

00:13:04.632 --> 00:13:07.092
mit tsvangen zey heysn zey,

00:13:07.092 --> 00:13:08.974
veyst dokh a bafel fun a doytsh,

00:13:08.974 --> 00:13:12.152
zoln onshraybn gute brivn arayn in geto arayn.

00:13:12.613 --> 00:13:18.614
un un di oylem, az eyner hot der oylem gants gevust az fort oyf arbet,

00:13:18.672 --> 00:13:20.406
esn zey trinken,

00:13:20.406 --> 00:13:22.229
zolt zikh shteln frayvilik,

00:13:22.229 --> 00:13:25.427
vayl zey hobn nisht gekent alts oyszukhn di ale lekher

00:13:25.427 --> 00:13:26.557
mit a mol

00:13:26.557 --> 00:13:30.051
vu di mentshn gefinen zikh, ken men nisht geyn, veyst vifl hayzer s'geven,

00:13:30.051 --> 00:13:32.194
toyznter yidishe hayzer.

00:13:32.194 --> 00:13:38.151
un mit kelers, mit boydem, un farmaskirte erter velkhe in shtubn zenen zey gevorn farmakht,

00:13:38.151 --> 00:13:41.078
un zey hobn zikh bahaltn, demolts zenen shoyn nisht geven keyn fraye

00:13:41.078 --> 00:13:44.031
fun fun arumgeyn handlen, shoyn der alts iz gevorn far-

00:13:44.031 --> 00:13:47.724
farshvundn, keyn shum reysh iz nisht geven, keyn shum esn nisht geven,

00:13:47.815 --> 00:13:51.960
far derfar zenen gefaln zeyer a sakh korbones, zeyer der oysgeshtorbn,

00:13:52.219 --> 00:13:57.056
du farshteyst? azoy iz tsugegangen dos lebn, ikh hob gearbet dort a lengere tsayt,

00:13:57.417 --> 00:14:02.864
di yor- s'heybt on di monatn rukn zikh, m'vayter un vayter, ven, vu, ven, vos iz shver,

00:14:02.864 --> 00:14:05.376
tsu UNK velkhes hayzer hot zikh ongehoybn.

00:14:05.382 --> 00:14:09.780
un zey hobn ongehoybn oystsuleydikn di dires fun di mentshn fun di kelern,

00:14:09.938 --> 00:14:14.348
zenen mir undz, di legale mentshn, arayn in di shtubn arayn, m'hot zikh aroysgenumen

00:14:14.348 --> 00:14:16.963
azelkhe v- v- vertike zakhn,

00:14:16.963 --> 00:14:20.380
un m'hot farkoyft, di shmuglers velkhe zey hobn zikh araynbakumen

00:14:20.380 --> 00:14:22.607
azelkhe ⟨partes⟩ fun di derfer,

00:14:22.607 --> 00:14:32.251
hobn zikh arayn- s'geven lekher in di vent, hobn zikh oysgearbet lekher, di politsey ven zey zenen geshtanen bay a lokh eyder m'hot es farmoyert, hot er genumen di gelt in di hant arayn,

00:14:32.251 --> 00:14:36.445
un zey hobn zikh adurkh gekhapt un zenen arayn dem Brauer SHOP vu ikh bin geven basheftikt

00:14:36.445 --> 00:14:38.855
undz hobn gehat un zey hobn arayngebrengt esn.

00:14:38.912 --> 00:14:41.794
zey hobn arayngebrengt fleysh, zey hobn arayngebrengt a shtikl broyt,

00:14:41.794 --> 00:14:43.802
zey hobn araynge- m'hot gekent zikh ernern,

00:14:43.802 --> 00:14:45.971
iz in di tsayt ven m'iz geven in dem

00:14:45.971 --> 00:14:47.532
in dem Brauer SHOP,

00:14:47.532 --> 00:14:49.160
hot men zikh, hot men gelebt.

00:14:49.160 --> 00:14:51.421
ruik iz geven, m'hot nisht gekhapt undz,

00:14:51.421 --> 00:14:54.735
m'hot gekent krign a bisl esn fun di fun di polyakn

00:14:54.758 --> 00:14:55.919
vos zenen arayn,

00:14:55.919 --> 00:14:57.823
azoy s'nisht geven azoy shlakht.

00:14:59.128 --> 00:15:05.099
iz vi azoy s'iz tsugegangen dos gantse, dos iz dokh nisht geven keyn tog un keyn monat un keyn yor.

00:15:04.022 --> 00:15:05.690
neyn. farshtey.

00:15:05.099 --> 00:15:08.896
azoy az ikh ikh halt shoyn vi ikh halt shoyn bald barn dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:15:08.896 --> 00:15:12.386
du farshteyst? ikh ken vayter geyn oyb du vilst,

00:15:11.717 --> 00:15:15.899
ikh vil dir fregn koydem IF m'hot gekrigt

00:15:15.899 --> 00:15:19.924
tsaytung mit nayes FROM aroysn,

00:15:19.924 --> 00:15:24.756
IF m'hot gehobt a yidishe kultur lebn in di shvere tsaytn.

00:15:24.390 --> 00:15:25.070
ver?

00:15:25.070 --> 00:15:28.180
di kultur mentshn zenen geven di ershte korbones.

00:15:28.508 --> 00:15:31.213
zey hobn gevust az a kultur mentsh hot a

00:15:31.213 --> 00:15:32.990
koyekh tsu organizirn.

00:15:33.418 --> 00:15:36.486
a durkhshnitlekhe mentsh, a niderike klas mentsh,

00:15:36.486 --> 00:15:37.901
hot nisht dem kraft

00:15:38.076 --> 00:15:40.891
eyns s'geven a groys hunger, hobn hobn zey genumen,

00:15:40.891 --> 00:15:43.397
di khevre, dos iz nokh geven fr- gants fri,

00:15:43.397 --> 00:15:47.194
un zey hobn mir aroyfgekhapt zikh aroyf-, zey hobn gehat ale adresn,

00:15:47.194 --> 00:15:51.708
vu vu di gelernte voynen, veyst, advokatn, doktoyrim,

00:15:51.708 --> 00:15:53.361
muziker, azelkhe

00:15:53.361 --> 00:15:57.020
mentshn velkhe zenen geven bale-parnose, un s'geven kulturele mentshn.

00:15:57.128 --> 00:15:58.998
azoy zey zenen aroyfgekumen

00:15:58.998 --> 00:16:04.986
in di shtubn vu di mentshn hobn gevoynt, in mitn bay der nakht, geklapt di tir arayn, veyst dokh vi azoy zey kumen, m'zol trefn mentshn

00:16:05.160 --> 00:16:08.782
in shlof, az nisht ke- bay tog ken er dokh zayn in gas,

00:16:09.210 --> 00:16:12.612
un m'hot im aropgenumen un hintn in toyer hot men im geshosn.

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:15.290
iz geven azelkhe faln keseyder.

00:16:15.290 --> 00:16:19.071
di ale kulturele khevre, a khuts vos m'hot nisht gerirt dem yudnrat,

00:16:19.071 --> 00:16:20.834
vos zey zenen geven di firers

00:16:20.834 --> 00:16:23.331
az m'zol tsushteln transportn, yidn,

00:16:23.331 --> 00:16:24.780
tsum umshlag plats.

00:16:24.803 --> 00:16:27.297
un keygn dem du host mir gerufn kultur

00:16:27.297 --> 00:16:30.585
mentshn, vu iz geven kultur? zey hobn dos oysgerotn

00:16:30.928 --> 00:16:32.508
vu s'iz nor geven a shtikl.

00:16:32.751 --> 00:16:40.232
un koydem hostu gez- gezogt az du host gekent Adam Tshernovski, der hoypt

00:16:40.232 --> 00:16:42.043
mentsh fun di yudnrat?

00:16:42.066 --> 00:16:44.710
tsi ikh hob gekent? absolut nisht.

00:16:42.960 --> 00:16:44.371
oyb du host im,

00:16:44.445 --> 00:16:45.249
neyn.

00:16:45.357 --> 00:16:47.038
nisht perzenish.

00:16:46.251 --> 00:16:50.956
ikh hob nisht gekent dort in gantsn un zey hobn nor gegebn dem bafel tsu tsushteln zikh tsu di

00:16:50.956 --> 00:16:53.723
POLICE STATION, di POLICE STATION hot undz aroysgeshtelt,

00:16:53.723 --> 00:16:57.213
zey hobn gegebn a bafel di POLICE STATION un undz hobn zikh geshtelt zey,

00:16:57.237 --> 00:17:00.083
azoy az m'hot un keyn shum kontakt nisht gehat mit zey.

00:17:00.190 --> 00:17:02.698
s'geven azoy vi a regirung iz geven.

00:17:03.278 --> 00:17:07.806
a kleyntshike reigrungl in geto, vos zey zoln onfirn az di doytshn zol zayn laykht,

00:17:07.806 --> 00:17:09.873
zoln zikh nisht perzenlekh darfn zikh,

00:17:09.873 --> 00:17:12.907
in di doy- di yidn veln shoyn tsushteln dos vos zey badarfn.

00:17:13.453 --> 00:17:19.061
un yedere mentsh hot zikh moyre gehat, der yudnrat hot dokh oykh moyre gehat far zikh, dervayl lebt er, di froyen lebn, di kinder lebn,

00:17:19.061 --> 00:17:22.343
dos viln fun lebn kenstu nisht bagrayfn,

00:17:22.343 --> 00:17:24.807
du kenst nisht farshteyn nisht zeyendik in aza.

00:17:24.807 --> 00:17:26.714
dos viln in lebn iz geven

00:17:26.714 --> 00:17:28.179
kenst zikh nisht forshteln.

00:17:28.692 --> 00:17:31.996
m'hot getun ruzhne zakhn azelkhe vos m'tut nisht

00:17:31.996 --> 00:17:34.609
in normal in a in a in a mentshlekhn

00:17:34.682 --> 00:17:36.397
a mentshlekhn veg.

00:17:36.522 --> 00:17:38.085
azoy az s'iz

00:17:38.226 --> 00:17:40.262
der geto der Varshever

00:17:40.420 --> 00:17:42.051
iz geven an oysnam.

00:17:42.141 --> 00:17:43.147
shreklekh.

00:17:43.761 --> 00:17:46.640
hunderter hunderter mentshn zenen gelign in di gasn.

00:17:47.895 --> 00:17:49.779
hot zikh a froy genumen dos lebn,

00:17:49.870 --> 00:17:51.939
vi azoy? iz aroysgegangen bay der nakht

00:17:52.300 --> 00:17:55.258
fun shtub aroys mit di shtul, a shtul, a CHAIR,

00:17:55.258 --> 00:17:59.966
avekgezetst zikh, s'geven a groyse frost vinter, s'a dort iz nishto azelkhe frest vi do,

00:17:59.966 --> 00:18:03.316
dortn iz do bay a draysik, finef un tsvontsik, zibn un tsvontsik,

00:18:03.316 --> 00:18:08.021
azoy hot zi zikh avekgezetst, zi hot gevolt aynshlofn, in frost shloft men ayn zeyer laykht,

00:18:08.213 --> 00:18:19.412
un zikh avekgeleygt gekhapt a drimele, in der fri bin ikh aroys oyfn mark aroys, geb ikh a k- a froy zitst zikh in mitn der gas oyf a shtul! vinter, a kelt, m'geyt tsu zi iz a shtayf, zitsndikerheyt eyn shtik.

00:18:21.004 --> 00:18:21.926
geven faln.

00:18:23.991 --> 00:18:26.668
azoy az s'iz geven a a shvere lebn.

00:18:27.923 --> 00:18:32.254
yo, nokh dem kumt men tsu shoyn vayter a dos ven m'heybt op tsu likvidirn.

00:18:32.462 --> 00:18:37.130
di vi nokh heysn zey di di fabrikn, m'likvidirt zey nisht un m'heyst

00:18:37.288 --> 00:18:40.331
di mentshn, oyb m'vet onheybn shoyn fun di lagern

00:18:40.331 --> 00:18:41.943
vil ikh do farendikn

00:18:41.943 --> 00:18:43.723
mit dem vi azoy m'hot im,

00:18:43.723 --> 00:18:46.237
zey hobn gekrign a bafel m'zol makhn

00:18:46.237 --> 00:18:47.846
Varshe yudnreyn.

00:18:48.426 --> 00:18:52.453
az keyn shum fabrikn, keyn doytshishe, gornisht ekzistirn,

00:18:52.560 --> 00:18:53.921
alts zol vern

00:18:53.995 --> 00:18:56.210
evakuirt fun Varshe.

00:18:56.210 --> 00:18:59.405
farshteyt zikh in ale lagern arayn in di kontsentratsyes lager.

00:18:59.817 --> 00:19:05.531
azoy az undz hobn mir bakumen a bafel, veyst dokh di firers fun fi varshtatn,

00:19:05.638 --> 00:19:07.420
az oykh geven yidn,

00:19:07.815 --> 00:19:11.606
dos hobn fakhlayt vos hobn badorfn onfirn mit di arbet,

00:19:12.152 --> 00:19:16.213
iz zey hobn gekrign a bafel az mir zoln ale zikh shteln

00:19:16.422 --> 00:19:18.224
in a gevisn gegnt,

00:19:18.224 --> 00:19:22.473
etlekhe gasn iz geven zeyer a sakh mentshn, s'geven fun kleynem geto mentshn,

00:19:22.598 --> 00:19:26.608
m'zol zikh dort shteln, ale in di un di tsayt tsu morgns,

00:19:27.289 --> 00:19:29.983
iz geven mentshn velkhe zey hobn zikh

00:19:30.225 --> 00:19:35.062
zeyere baheltenishn shoyn gehat, zey hobn ge- m'hot gevust az m'geyt in di lagern arayn,

00:19:35.170 --> 00:19:36.851
un zey hobn zikh bahaltn.

00:19:37.296 --> 00:19:38.558
bay mir in

00:19:38.558 --> 00:19:43.410
tsum bayshpil, in dem varshtat vu undz ikh hob gearbet bay Brauer,

00:19:43.410 --> 00:19:45.002
hot mayn shvoger

00:19:45.193 --> 00:19:48.410
zikh gemakht a baheltenish in der heykh vu er hot gearbet.

00:19:48.653 --> 00:19:51.144
geven zeyer azoy fil shtubn iz geven,

00:19:51.488 --> 00:19:52.421
un aher,

00:19:52.421 --> 00:19:56.122
iz hot er zikh gema- un tsugerukt zikh, ikh veys, er hot gemakht zikh a lokh,

00:19:56.382 --> 00:19:59.576
in in di tir zol zikh kenen araynshtupn,

00:19:59.576 --> 00:20:02.805
mit di froy, mit a kind, a kleyn kind hot er gehat,

00:20:02.997 --> 00:20:06.805
un er hot zikh gemakht bahelt- ma- ken zayn az zey ebn aroyfkumen

00:20:06.844 --> 00:20:12.255
m'heyst ale aropgeyn, zey ebn aroyfkumen, zey ebn gebn a kuk di shtubn zenen leydik, ebn zey avekgeyn.

00:20:12.345 --> 00:20:13.993
dos hot er zikh ayngeredt.

00:20:15.282 --> 00:20:18.921
z- dos iz geven nakher a tsore mit di shtubn vayter arayn.

00:20:19.382 --> 00:20:23.209
far derfar s'geven zeyer a sakh, hunderter hunderter mentshn hobn zikh gemakht

00:20:23.209 --> 00:20:25.096
baheltenishn in di hayzer.

00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:32.184
afilek in di kelern vu zey hobn nor gehat arayntsugeyn, m'hot ongehoybn tsu boyen nokh tsu der tsayt, bunkers zeyer a sakh iz geven.

00:20:32.697 --> 00:20:37.601
un zey hobn ongehoybn dort tsunoyftsunemen dos bisl mentshn, m'zol makhn reyn

00:20:38.046 --> 00:20:39.390
oys arbet,

00:20:39.784 --> 00:20:41.856
nu, tsunoyfgenumen mentshn,

00:20:41.856 --> 00:20:43.679
vos hot pasirt veys ikh nisht,

00:20:43.679 --> 00:20:44.925
m'hot ongehoybn

00:20:45.235 --> 00:20:48.050
fun di, s'geven hunderter mentshn, grupes,

00:20:48.050 --> 00:20:50.513
hot men ongehoybn aroystsunemen mentshn

00:20:50.513 --> 00:20:52.299
velkhe zenen geven shoyn nisht ke-

00:20:52.542 --> 00:20:54.572
oysgemordevet fun hunger,

00:20:54.572 --> 00:20:56.299
un geshtelt oyf eyn zayt.

00:20:56.423 --> 00:20:58.847
un a mentsh vos er hot nokh oysgezen mentshlekh,

00:20:58.853 --> 00:21:01.952
heyst es mit koyekh, avekgeshtelt in der tsveyter zayt.

00:21:01.975 --> 00:21:05.361
froyen, avekgeshtelt in di zayt, mener in di zayt,

00:21:05.704 --> 00:21:08.752
azoy az m'hot gevust az dos iz korbones.

00:21:09.028 --> 00:21:11.874
oder nisht shisn, oder geyn in di lagern arayn.

00:21:12.285 --> 00:21:15.249
azoy ikh bin geven tsvishn a grupe, ikh bin nokh geven

00:21:15.711 --> 00:21:17.443
ikh hob nokh, ikh bin nokh geven fizish

00:21:17.652 --> 00:21:19.164
tsu arbetn,

00:21:19.542 --> 00:21:23.771
in algemeyn bin ikh a mol far di krig geven zeyer fizish, in der sport gants UNK.

00:21:24.081 --> 00:21:28.040
azoy az dos hot mir a bisl gehaltn oyf di fis mit di lagern oykhet.

00:21:28.705 --> 00:21:34.616
du farshteyst? hob ikh, hot men dortn opgeteylt di grupn, zey di grupn vos s'geven di in eyn zayt

00:21:34.616 --> 00:21:39.010
zenen avekgef- marsherirt gevorn, vu ahin, mistam tsum umshlag-plats,

00:21:39.133 --> 00:21:42.670
un undz hot men geheysn tsurikgeyn in di varshtatn arayn.

00:21:43.335 --> 00:21:45.556
ze ikh do az m'lozt undz nokh lebn,

00:21:45.850 --> 00:21:48.116
farshteyst, der shvoger iz dort geven.

00:21:48.116 --> 00:21:52.723
nor ven hot er zikh gemakht dos baheltenish? ven m'hot shoyn gekrign dem letstn bafel yudnreyn

00:21:52.723 --> 00:21:54.596
hot er zikh gemakht dos baheltenish.

00:21:54.596 --> 00:21:56.003
un ikh hob tsufelik

00:21:56.042 --> 00:21:59.039
geven azoy vi, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn tsutrit tsu dem.

00:21:59.265 --> 00:22:02.060
tsu dem baheltenish vu der shvoger iz geven.

00:22:02.117 --> 00:22:04.915
hob ikh mikh gezogt tsu mayn froy, veystu vos, m'vet aropgeyn,

00:22:04.915 --> 00:22:07.936
ikh hob gevust fun a sakh erter vos s'iz geven bunkers,

00:22:07.936 --> 00:22:10.931
beydem, boydem, zakhn bahaltn,

00:22:10.931 --> 00:22:14.188
un ikh bin mir arayn, ikh hob gevoynt akht un tsvontsik,

00:22:14.188 --> 00:22:19.124
bin ikh arayn mit der froy, dem shvoger hob ikh gezogt az undz geyen mir arop zukhn ergets andersh vu tsu zayn,

00:22:19.124 --> 00:22:20.454
tsu bahaltn zikh,

00:22:20.629 --> 00:22:25.989
un ze'mir arayn in iz geven Frentshishkano draysik, a tsveyter hoyf,

00:22:26.046 --> 00:22:30.275
yeder hoyf hot dokh gehat bay a zeks, akht kamenitses, finef, zeks shtokedike,

00:22:30.518 --> 00:22:32.824
groyse hayzer, un dortn arayn,

00:22:32.830 --> 00:22:34.489
hob ikh ongehoybn

00:22:34.489 --> 00:22:37.357
tsu zukhn a a bunker, a baheltenish,

00:22:37.357 --> 00:22:39.489
oyser dem shtibele in der heykh.

00:22:39.698 --> 00:22:41.222
vu s'zol nor nisht zayn.

00:22:41.222 --> 00:22:44.993
zukhn, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn tsutrit tsu di UNK, ikh hob gevust zey ebn dort epes makhn,

00:22:44.993 --> 00:22:48.197
az dortn zenen geven yidn, m'vet azoy zukhn az m'vet gefinen.

00:22:48.405 --> 00:22:49.918
der shvoger hot nisht gevolt.

00:22:49.924 --> 00:22:51.369
er hot gehat a kleyn kind,

00:22:52.607 --> 00:22:57.832
iz bin ikh arayn in dem hoyf arayn, bin mir aroyfgegangen, hintn in keler hob ikh gornisht gezen,

00:22:57.923 --> 00:23:00.515
ikh bin mir aroyfgegangen oyf der heykh oyfn letstn shtokene,

00:23:00.555 --> 00:23:04.130
un arumgegangen di letste shtok in azan dire arayn iz geven

00:23:04.130 --> 00:23:06.878
oysgeleydikt, farshteyt zikh keyn mentsh iz shoyn nisht geven,

00:23:07.170 --> 00:23:10.252
un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu zukhn epes a a lokh,

00:23:10.360 --> 00:23:13.866
a shtibele a bahaltene un vos un bin mir arayn in tualet arayn

00:23:13.866 --> 00:23:17.255
tsufelik, tu- zukhn, hob ikh gezen oyfn sufitl

00:23:17.295 --> 00:23:18.490
dem CEILING

00:23:18.490 --> 00:23:23.663
in der heykh, ot sh- ot mit keyn shpares nisht, nor s'azoy shelne geven farmakht

00:23:23.663 --> 00:23:25.763
nor ikh hob ikh zikh derkhapt az dortn

00:23:25.763 --> 00:23:27.684
dos iz a tirele oyftsuefenen.

00:23:28.315 --> 00:23:31.973
farshteyst? un ikh hob ongehoybn, ikh hob gevust, ikh hob gekent di shkheynim,

00:23:31.973 --> 00:23:34.530
un eynem fun di shkheynim hob ikh gevust dem nomen,

00:23:34.530 --> 00:23:37.736
bin mir aroyfgegangen oyf dem benkl vu m'zitst in der tualet,

00:23:37.736 --> 00:23:40.233
un ikh hob ongehoybn aroyf tsu shrayen tsu im,

00:23:40.233 --> 00:23:42.433
"Teytlboym, zolstu visn Birman

00:23:42.507 --> 00:23:45.370
iz do do un er hot nisht vu ahin tsu tun zikh,

00:23:45.510 --> 00:23:46.888
mit der froy,

00:23:46.978 --> 00:23:49.469
un ze undz aroyf tsu nemen."

00:23:49.830 --> 00:23:53.401
keyner hot zikh nisht ongerufn, m'hot gemeynt m'meynt nisht zey,

00:23:53.678 --> 00:23:58.948
zey hobn gevust a yid shrayt, un m'ruft nokh Teytlboym hot er geheysn, er iz geven a mekler bay leder,

00:23:58.948 --> 00:24:00.489
ikh hob im gekent zeyer gut,

00:24:00.900 --> 00:24:04.879
un er hot mir, un s- ikh hob gevust ikh vel nisht avekgeyn,

00:24:04.879 --> 00:24:09.197
"efn oyf dos tirele, un z- ikh hob nisht vu tsu loyfn, ikh hob nisht keyn baheltenish,"

00:24:09.557 --> 00:24:14.633
un zey hobn mir arop gelozt di leyter, nokh a gevise ikh veys tsen minut, tsi fuftsn, zey hobn gezen az zey ebn gornisht oyftun,

00:24:14.633 --> 00:24:19.389
ikh eb shteyn shrayen ebn zey oykhet nokh araynfaln, azoy az zey hobn mikh aroyfgenumen in der heykh arayn.

00:24:19.564 --> 00:24:24.654
iz geven sheyn bisl familyes zenen zikh gelegn yeder opgeteylt fun eyn familyen un tsveytn.

00:24:25.065 --> 00:24:27.303
oyfn sufit hobn gehongen zek,

00:24:27.580 --> 00:24:29.244
mit sukhares,

00:24:29.250 --> 00:24:31.871
getriknte broyt.

00:24:31.871 --> 00:24:35.297
az zoln nisht vern farshimlt, zoln nisht vern fardart,

00:24:35.297 --> 00:24:37.406
a nisht fardart, m'zol zey kenen meln.

00:24:37.406 --> 00:24:41.962
gantse zek oyfgehongen. di khevre gobn zikh geshikevet a lange tsayt

00:24:41.962 --> 00:24:43.014
zikh tsu

00:24:43.662 --> 00:24:48.054
az m'zol hobn oyf dem boydem a fal, zey hobn nisht gevust az s'vet geshen azan brokh nakher,

00:24:48.054 --> 00:24:50.625
vos m'hot veyst dokh untergetsundn ale hayzer.

00:24:50.783 --> 00:24:53.004
iz hobn zikh di zek.

00:24:53.044 --> 00:24:56.795
un zey hobn hobn zey mir opgeteylt a a opteylung mit di froy,

00:24:56.795 --> 00:25:00.632
un gelign zikh dort ikh veys oyf zek gelegn oyf der erd oyfn boydem.

00:25:00.722 --> 00:25:03.500
ikh bin geven gliklekh m'iz opgeteylt fun di gantse khevre.

00:25:03.912 --> 00:25:08.394
un shoyn un der un vu vu der shvoger iz ahingekumen veys ikh nisht,

00:25:08.502 --> 00:25:11.047
nor s'a nakher bin ikh gevoyer gevorn.

00:25:11.047 --> 00:25:12.329
iz

00:25:12.329 --> 00:25:15.408
yo bin ikh dort gelegn, dervayl s'hot zikh ongehoybn

00:25:15.408 --> 00:25:17.473
di oyfshtand, di nayntstn

00:25:19.858 --> 00:25:21.725
HOW WAS THE,

00:25:21.968 --> 00:25:23.582
di ferte khoydesh,

00:25:23.773 --> 00:25:24.796
APRIL.

00:25:24.567 --> 00:25:28.217
APRIL. di mayse fun APRIL, dos iz geven di tsayt fun peysekh.

00:25:28.217 --> 00:25:32.891
zey hobn gekhapt di yidn, UNK di yidishe spetsyel, hargenen un khapn

00:25:32.891 --> 00:25:35.799
un mordeven, nor in di yidishe yom-toyvim, UNK.

00:25:34.405 --> 00:25:36.435
vos far vos far a yor?

00:25:36.345 --> 00:25:37.233
bite?

00:25:36.435 --> 00:25:37.751
v- vi

00:25:37.751 --> 00:25:39.697
vos far a yor? ven?

00:25:39.197 --> 00:25:44.169
dos iz shoyn geven dray un fertsikstn yor, nayntstn febru-

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:41.841
dray un fertsik.

00:25:43.652 --> 00:25:45.333
APRIL, april.

00:25:44.260 --> 00:25:48.877
APRIL, april, yo in fertstn, nayntstn april gedenk ikh vi haynt

00:25:49.103 --> 00:25:50.509
iz

00:25:50.509 --> 00:25:51.825
iz dortn

00:25:51.825 --> 00:25:53.754
hot zikh ongehoybn

00:25:53.980 --> 00:25:57.014
di di di organizatsyes yidishe

00:25:57.014 --> 00:25:59.140
hobn zikh ongehoybn tsu ba- fareynikn

00:25:59.140 --> 00:26:01.553
der Bund, un Yunge Paletsien,

00:26:01.553 --> 00:26:05.173
zenen geven ongezeene mentshn velkhe zey hobn gekent organizirn deys.

00:26:05.173 --> 00:26:09.381
un zey hobn gehat a kontakt mit di oyserlekhe velt, dos heyst mit di kristn.

00:26:09.589 --> 00:26:14.358
zey hobn gevust az m'vet batsoln, undz hobn mir dem gantsn raykhtum fun di gekhapte mentshn.

00:26:14.550 --> 00:26:19.010
di vilde mentshn, di dires zenen geven ful ongepakt mit futers mit andere

00:26:19.010 --> 00:26:20.884
ontuekhtser, hemder

00:26:20.884 --> 00:26:23.521
farshteyst? un di kristn hobn genosn fun derfun.

00:26:23.730 --> 00:26:28.367
azoy az az az zey hobn gevust az m'ken do onheybn handlen.

00:26:28.367 --> 00:26:30.947
undz hobn mir gehat mit vos tsu handlen demolts.

00:26:31.290 --> 00:26:35.806
farhsteyst? ah iz vu bin ikh demol- yo un geven in der heykh,

00:26:35.914 --> 00:26:39.716
un az m'hot hob ikh aroysgekrign di, di nakht ven s'geven

00:26:39.716 --> 00:26:44.413
ven m'hot gevust az s'vet zikh do shikeven an oyfshtand, m'hot shoyn gehert klangen,

00:26:44.571 --> 00:26:48.800
hot men aroysge- bin ikh arop bay der nakht, ikh aleyn, di froy iz geven in der heykh,

00:26:48.807 --> 00:26:51.385
oyf dem boydem, ikh bin arop bay der nakht,

00:26:51.385 --> 00:26:54.791
un tsugegangen tsu dem toyer vu s'iz geven dos lokh aroystsukukn,

00:26:54.831 --> 00:26:56.127
hob ikh gezen

00:26:56.127 --> 00:26:57.899
vi unter di vent

00:26:57.899 --> 00:26:59.111
sharn zikh

00:26:59.151 --> 00:27:02.216
a gantse sha- reye yidn,

00:27:02.678 --> 00:27:07.197
herst, zenen afile geven mit helmen a sakh, ven undz zenen mir oy- oyf gere-

00:27:07.197 --> 00:27:10.462
oysgeglaykht di helmen vos zenen gekumen fun front

00:27:10.462 --> 00:27:14.467
hobn zey a sakh, vi loyt vi loyt vi ikh hob gezen oyf dem fentsterl.

00:27:14.507 --> 00:27:17.336
az sharn zikh un sharn zikh m'zol zey nisht bamerkn.

00:27:17.595 --> 00:27:22.114
un hot men gevust az s'vet zayn yontev tsu morgns, s'vet zayn a tsore.

00:27:22.114 --> 00:27:24.997
undz hobn mir gevust fun dem az zey shikeven zikh tsu an oyfshtand.

00:27:25.358 --> 00:27:28.080
nor di organizatsyes, m'hot nisht keynemen tsugenumen

00:27:28.080 --> 00:27:30.990
nisht fun keyn organizatsyes, zey hobn nisht gehat keyn tsutrit.

00:27:30.990 --> 00:27:34.700
ikh vel dir zogn m'zol es, tsvishn undz zol es blaybn, s'geven a bisl mosrim oykhet.

00:27:34.960 --> 00:27:38.970
tsvishn di yidn, zey hobn azoy m'hot hot men moyre gehat, zey zenen geven gut organizirt.

00:27:39.145 --> 00:27:43.656
un zey hobn araynbakumen fun oysern geto fun dem esnvarg vos m'hot gehat UNK,

00:27:43.656 --> 00:27:45.585
UNK m'hot arayngeshikt gever.

00:27:45.793 --> 00:27:47.840
arayngeshikt gever, m'hot di granatn,

00:27:47.840 --> 00:27:52.368
farshteyst, un zey hobn zikh oysgearbet di kokteyln un BOTTLES oykhet,

00:27:52.459 --> 00:27:55.637
un azoy s'iz un bald in der fri hot zikh gemakht

00:27:55.637 --> 00:27:57.583
der arayngang fun di doytshn

00:27:57.673 --> 00:27:59.371
yudnreyn der geto.

00:28:00.542 --> 00:28:02.915
yudnreyn, hostu badorfn zen vos dortn

00:28:02.938 --> 00:28:05.395
mit azan koyekh zey zenen arayn.

00:28:05.402 --> 00:28:09.851
koydem zenen zey gegangen ale oysgeshtelt far eyn vayz mit dem lid

00:28:09.857 --> 00:28:13.836
"dos yudn-blut oyf dem meser shprotst," veyst vos dos heyst,

00:28:13.836 --> 00:28:16.348
az dos der dos blut fun a yid

00:28:16.860 --> 00:28:20.144
iz oyfn meser vos er hot in di di bagnet in

00:28:20.421 --> 00:28:22.727
un dos iz geven zeyer lid baym arayngang,

00:28:24.015 --> 00:28:30.264
un yo, un zey hobn zikh arayngelozt in geto arayn, s'hot ongehoybn tsu makhn zikh, m'hot ongehoybn tsu shisn in ale fentster arayn,

00:28:30.264 --> 00:28:31.654
der ershter tsugang.

00:28:31.963 --> 00:28:33.765
di khevre zenen gelegn,

00:28:33.765 --> 00:28:36.682
dort iz geven oyf di Shvindeyoske zenen geven

00:28:36.739 --> 00:28:39.216
UNK azan opteylung fun di doytshn

00:28:39.216 --> 00:28:41.427
un s'geven a barshtn SHOP

00:28:41.427 --> 00:28:42.572
m'hot oysgearbet

00:28:42.662 --> 00:28:45.508
BRUSHES, groyse barshtn ruzhnerley,

00:28:45.784 --> 00:28:49.558
un zey zenen arayn in di BUILDING UNK vu der SHOP iz geven.

00:28:49.851 --> 00:28:54.176
zey hobn efsher oysgerat vu di doytshn zenen gekumen, efsher hobn di polyakn gegebn

00:28:54.176 --> 00:28:57.585
a a a a a ORDER, nisht a ORDER, aza

00:28:57.585 --> 00:29:00.796
zog az in dem gegnt geyen arayn di ershte transportn.

00:29:00.820 --> 00:29:03.246
farshteyst? un zey hobn zikh dortn zikh

00:29:03.246 --> 00:29:05.724
lokirt zikh oyf di dekher,

00:29:05.781 --> 00:29:07.786
arayn in di hayzer arayn,

00:29:07.786 --> 00:29:12.221
fun di bershtn SHOP UNK, mit ale o- mit di mit di gevern,

00:29:12.396 --> 00:29:15.765
un s'gegangen a fayer du kenst zikh nisht forshteln.

00:29:15.889 --> 00:29:19.581
s'zenen gefaln hunderter, hunderter ken ikh efsher ibergetribn,

00:29:19.581 --> 00:29:21.209
tsendlike doytshn

00:29:21.209 --> 00:29:23.935
iz gefaln mit di gevern mit alding.

00:29:23.935 --> 00:29:27.678
s'geven a groyse shkhite hobn zey gemakht. dos iz geven in ershtn tog.

00:29:28.478 --> 00:29:33.006
un nokh dem hobn zey gekrign a bafel zikh altsding tsurik aroys tsu tsien zikh fun geto,

00:29:33.006 --> 00:29:37.213
di gehargete hobn gehat bay zikh gever, m'hot nokh bay tsugenumen bay zey dos gever oykhet,

00:29:37.287 --> 00:29:39.390
azoy az m'hot alding gemakht leydik.

00:29:39.396 --> 00:29:42.140
pasirt hot es tsu morgns di tragedye,

00:29:42.383 --> 00:29:43.620
un m'vet

00:29:42.602 --> 00:29:43.696
zey zenen ge-

00:29:43.620 --> 00:29:44.486
m'vet

00:29:43.696 --> 00:29:44.202
ALRIGHT.

00:29:44.695 --> 00:29:46.275
m'vet endikn do.

00:29:46.365 --> 00:29:47.560
in der TAPE THREE.
